ography":"羅浩楷，原名羅浩鍇，香港資深男演員，前無綫電視基本藝人合約藝人。\n\n羅氏善於扮演各類人物，經典角色為於無綫電視《歡樂今宵》節目扮演呂奇及林子祥。他曾拜師許佩、張雲、林祥園老師名下，曾任職業琴手 20 多年的他，不但是位音樂歌唱導師（因向歌唱老師偷師而學曉一些歌唱技巧，所以嘗試自己開班教學。），也是位樂隊領班。另外，他亦曾擔任過無綫電視歌唱比賽甄選入圍參賽者階段的評判。\n\n2017 年 8 月與無綫電視結束合約，同時以半退休狀態淡出娛樂圈。","name":"羅浩楷","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"羅浩楷，原名羅浩鍇，香港資深男演員，前無綫電視基本藝人合約藝人。\n\n羅氏善於扮演各類人物，經典角色為於無綫電視《歡樂今宵》節目扮演呂奇及林子祥。他曾拜師許佩、張雲、林祥園老師名下，曾任職業琴手20多年的他，不但是位音樂歌唱導師（因向歌唱老師偷師而學曉一些歌唱技巧，所以嘗試自己開班教學。），也是位樂隊領班。另外，他亦曾擔任過無綫電視歌唱比賽甄選入圍參賽者階段的評判。\n\n2017年8月與無綫電視結束合約，同時以半退休狀態淡出娛樂圈。","name":"羅浩楷","primary":false}}]}},"person_2307978_translations":{"at":1772469965937,"data":{"id":2307978,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ex Piya Wimuktayon is an actor. He was named for Chulalongkorn Memorial Day, or Wan Piyamaharaj in Thai. He graduated from Chandrakasem Rajabhat University.","name":"Piya Vimuktayon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ปิยะ วิมุกตายน","primary":false}}]}},"person_5641479_translations":{"at":1772469967994,"data":{"id":5641479,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Konatsu Hirabayashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"平林瑚夏","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Konatsu Hirabayashi (平林 瑚夏, Hirabayashi Konatsu, nacida el 27 de agosto) es una actriz de voz (seiyu) japonesa de la pprefectura de Aichi. Está afiliada a Atomic Monkey. Habla el dialecto de Aichi y tiene grupo sanguíneo B. Sus aficiones y habilidades especiales incluyen cocinar, cantar, dibujar, coser, ver obras de teatro y la gimnasia rítmica.","name":"Konatsu Hirabayashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"平林瑚夏是日本的女性聲優。出身於愛知縣，所屬公司為 Atomic Monkey。","name":"平林瑚夏","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Konacu Hirabajaši","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Конацу Хирабаяши","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Конацу Хірабаяші","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"平林瑚夏是日本的女性聲優。出身於愛知縣，所屬公司為 Atomic Monkey。","name":"平林瑚夏","primary":false}}]}},"person_2375667_translations":{"at":1772469968493,"data":{"id":2375667,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Robério Diógenes (Parambu, July 18, 1963), is a Brazilian actor and cultural producer.","name":"Robério Diógenes","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Robério Diógenes","primary":true}}]}},"person_2663920_translations":{"at":1772469981951,"data":{"id":2663920,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Choi Young-jun is a South Korean actor and made his acting debut in 2019. Since then, he has appeared in a handful of television dramas.","name":"Choi Young-jun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"崔英俊","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"최영준","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"崔英俊（최영준，Choi Young-j